    <entry>
      <title>LaityH开发文档</title>
      <link href="/2021/08/06/laityhtool/"/>
      <url>/2021/08/06/laityhtool/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="LaityHTool项目简介"><a href="#LaityHTool项目简介" class="headerlink" title="LaityHTool项目简介"></a>LaityHTool项目简介</h3><p>LaityHTool是一个我自己想到什么功能就会加在上面的项目，运行于整个PC平台，预计会开发的功能大概有：</p><ol><li>Todo列表（实现云同步） <font color="red">√</font></li><li>BDownloader（B站下载器）<ul><li>收藏夹下载 <font color="red">√</font></li><li>AV/BV号下载</li><li>链接下载</li></ul></li><li>Spyder Center（服务器爬虫总控，监控服务器上和本机爬虫运行情况）</li><li>Note Reader（文本阅读器，支持普通笔记以及markdown文本）<br>…</li></ol><h4 id="技术简介"><a href="#技术简介" class="headerlink" title="技术简介"></a>技术简介</h4><p>采用Electron-vue前端技术，Electron是PC上跨平台的集成了V8+nodejs的采用前端开发语言的框架。Vue是前端的流行开发框架之一。</p><p>本项目的后端开发语言不定，目前还未进行到后端</p><h3 id="项目前端问题"><a href="#项目前端问题" class="headerlink" title="项目前端问题"></a>项目前端问题</h3><p>记录项目中查询过资料的前端问题</p><h4 id="初始化项目时需要更新官方模板中Electron和Node的版本"><a href="#初始化项目时需要更新官方模板中Electron和Node的版本" class="headerlink" title="初始化项目时需要更新官方模板中Electron和Node的版本"></a>初始化项目时需要更新官方模板中Electron和Node的版本</h4><p>命令行执行<br>yarn upgrade-interactive –latest</p><p>选择electron、electron-builder 、electron-debug、electron-devtools-installer这四项更新。然后修改electron主进程文件index.js中的创建主窗口代码为：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-javascript" data-language="javascript"><code class="language-javascript">mainWindow <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token keyword">new</span> <span class="token class-name">BrowserWindow</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span>  height<span class="token operator">:</span> xxx<span class="token punctuation">,</span>  useContentSize<span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token boolean">true</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>  width<span class="token operator">:</span> xxx<span class="token punctuation">,</span>  webPreferences<span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span>    nodeIntegration<span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token boolean">true</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token comment">//在网页中集成Node，electron高版本默认关闭</span>  <span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h4 id="Electron配置请求头的Referer"><a href="#Electron配置请求头的Referer" class="headerlink" title="Electron配置请求头的Referer"></a>Electron配置请求头的Referer</h4><p>由于请求B站下的资源需要请求中携带B站的Referer，而Referer是没有办法直接在axios中设置的，会抛出unsafe-header，因为浏览器不允许修改Referer，所以我们直接修改electorn即可，因为electron是提供浏览器环境的。在electron的主进程index.js中设置一下代码</p><pre class="line-numbers language-javascript" data-language="javascript"><code class="language-javascript"><span class="token keyword">const</span> bilibiliFilter <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span> <span class="token comment">// 当请求这些链接时需要携带Referer</span>  urls<span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token string">"https://*.bilibili.com/*"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token string">"http://*.bilibili.com/*"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token string">"http://*.hdslb.com/*"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token string">"https://*.bilivideo.com/*"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token string">"https://*/*"</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="token comment">// electron的session模块提供了在发送请求前修改请求头的方法 使用前需要导入session：const &#123; session &#125; = require('electron')</span>session<span class="token punctuation">.</span>defaultSession<span class="token punctuation">.</span>webRequest<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">onBeforeSendHeaders</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>bilibiliFilter<span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token parameter">details<span class="token punctuation">,</span> callback</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">=></span> <span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span>  details<span class="token punctuation">.</span>requestHeaders<span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token string">'Referer'</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token string">'http://www.bilibili.com'</span>  <span class="token function">callback</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span> requestHeaders<span class="token operator">:</span> details<span class="token punctuation">.</span>requestHeaders <span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h3 id="项目后端问题"><a href="#项目后端问题" class="headerlink" title="项目后端问题"></a>项目后端问题</h3>]]></content>
      
      
